screen_desc: The screenshot shows a screen from the Uber app asking the user to accept Uber's Terms of Use and review the Privacy Notice. The text states that by selecting "I Agree" below, the user confirms they have reviewed and agree to the Terms of Use and acknowledge the Privacy Notice, and that they are at least 18 years of age. There are two buttons at the bottom: one labeled "I Agree" and another labeled "Next." The screen also displays the time (11:00 AM) and various status icons at the top.
